  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PostFilter<Q extends Request,​S extends Response>
    Pipeline stage that filters a Request after a Response was generated.
    PostProcessor<Q extends Request,​S extends Response>
    Pipeline stage that processes a Request after the Response was already sent.
    PreFilter<Q extends Request>
    Pipeline stage that filters a Request before a Response is generated.
    RequestHandler<Q extends Request,​S extends Response>
    Stage of the Pipeline responsible for generating a Response.
    ResponseRenderer<S extends Response>
    Used to render a Response and generate the string that is sent as the http response body.
